  <brief_title>Reconstruction of Monocytic Immunocompetence by Granulocyte-macrophage-colony Stimulating Factor (GM-CSF) in Patients With Severe Sepsis and Septic Shock</brief_title>
  <official_title>Reconstruction of Monocytic Immunocompetence by Granulocyte-macrophage-colony Stimulating Factor (GM-CSF) in Patients With Severe Sepsis and Septic Shock: a Prospective, Randomised, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Study</official_title>
