  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      There is basic science evidence that GM-CSF reconstructs cellular immunity in septic
      patients. In this prospective, randomised double-blind, placebo-controlled trial, we
      investigate whether this can be achieved in patients with severe sepsis and septic shock.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      GM-CSF reconstructs cellular immunity in septic patients. In this prospective, randomised
      double-blind, placebo-controlled trial, we investigate whether this can be achieved in
      patinets with severe sepsis and septic shock.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
